(define/contract (good-subsetof-binary-matrix grid)
  (-> (listof (listof exact-integer?)) (listof exact-integer?))

  (define (check-column-sums subset)
    (let* ((subset-length (length subset))
           (column-sums (for/list ([j (length (first grid))])
                          (for/sum ([i subset]) (list-ref (list-ref grid i) j)))))
      (for/or ([sum column-sums])
        (> sum (floor (/ subset-length 2))))))
  
  (define (good-subsets indices)
    (define (helper remaining current)
      (if (null? remaining)
          (if (and (not (null? current)) (not (check-column-sums current)))
              (list current)
              '())
          (append (helper (cdr remaining) current)
                  (helper (cdr remaining) (cons (car remaining) current)))))
    (helper indices '()))

  (let* ((indices (range (length grid)))
         (subsets (good-subsets indices)))
    (if (null? subsets) '() (car subsets))))
